0 "" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 
-1 49 "What does that \"\{x=x\}\" mean?   It's simple this: " }}{PARA 
