-1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 32 "So, if we choose m = 200 we get
:" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 
